    "In practice, we suggest = 64 for all the learned indexes internally utilizing PGM-Index, as this value effectively balances index Index update efficiency evaluation (Q7)In this section, we evaluate the update efficiency for learned indexes that support dynamic operations (i.e., LISA, RSMI, and IFI).",
    "For each dataset, we first construct an index using the initial 80% of the points.",
